Why are students encouraged to learn CS?
They are encouraged to learn cs because it is a growuing field. So the older 
people/people who made it want us to understand how it works that way we can 
make it better and easier to use. For them And for us.

What should students learn from CS?
Students should in Cs how computers work and how they work together to do other
things on a computer than use google and play minecraft or CS Go.
